metadata.name: Wei Sempai #1
metadata.description: Wei Warriors Genesis is a collection of 888 degen warriors that reside on the ethereum blockchain. The Wei warrior project is a community driven project that loves to participate in games and activities also known as the Wei games. Wei warriors aim to bring authenticated merch to local web3 communities making the merch aspect more cost efficient for both the founders and their communities. A portion of the revenue will go to the Wei warrior community wallet to fund the Wei games and other Web3 and IRL events.
